angular basics -> 2022

-----------
$ npx -p @angular/cli ng new proj-name --style=scss
-----------

generator -> @angular/cli
	2 mins required to created angular app
	
	Install @angular/cli
		- install npm by installing node
			- download and install nodejs
			- node -v (14 =+ is required)
			- npm -v
		- npm install @angular/cli@12.x -g
		- npm install -g @angular/cli
			only for virtual machines
			C:\Users\123\AppData\Roaming\npm
				add this path to PATH environment variable 
				C:\Users\123\AppData\Roaming\npm
		- ng version
		- Create angular project
		- ng new project-name
		
		
